---
title: Spaghetti and Turkey Meatballs with Parmesan, Kale & Tomatoes
description: Spaghetti with creamy tomato sauce is always a recipe for success. Is there anyone who’d turn down a plate of noodles piled high and dusted with cheese? Surely not, although adding some extra meat and veg certainly makes it all the more crave-able. Which is exactly what we’re doing: taking a tried-and-true Italian American classic and adding hearty turkey meatballs and bites of chewy kale.
